{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-89","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 89","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete stvoriti prideve koji pokazuju najviši stepen nečega. Ovo su superlativni pridevi (superlative adjectives). Oni pokazuju da ništa drugo ne može nadmašiti određeni stepen.</p>\n<p>Za kratke prideve, dodaju se segment <span class=\"highlighted-text\">the</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-est</span> na kraju reči. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">She enjoys her weekdays to the fullest</span> (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">the</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">full</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">est</span>).</p>\n<p>Za duge prideve, stvara se najviši stepen dodavanjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">the most</span> pre prideva. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">This is the most interesting book I've read</span> (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">the most</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">interesting</span>).</p>\n<p>Ovo je uvod u ove prideve. Naučićete više kasnije.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"","explanation":null,"challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","block":"learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-89"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>So many activities. I don't think I could keep up that pace. But it's nice to know you enjoy it to BLANK, Maria.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"the fullest","feedback":"<p>Ovo je vrsta najvišeg standarda za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">full</span>. Ne zaboravite odeljak.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-parking.png","characte